      "text": "# 知识树可视化 Implementation Plan\n\n> **For agentic workers:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:subagent-driven-development (recommended) or superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task. Steps use checkbox (`- [ ]`) syntax for tracking.\n\n**Goal:** 在 edu-cloud Web 平台内构建交互式知识树页面，教师通过 Agent 完善图谱，家长直观看到孩子掌握度。\n\n**Architecture:** 投影同步（knowledge.db → PostgreSQL）+ FastAPI 后端（3 端点 + 1 Agent 工具）+ Vue 3 前端（AntV G6 力导向图 + 树形导航），同组件多角色权限控制。\n\n**Tech Stack:** FastAPI, SQLAlchemy 2.0 async, Alembic, Vue 3 + Naive UI + AntV G6 v5, pytest\n\n**Design:** `docs/plans/2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-design.md`\n\n---\n\n## File Structure\n\n### Backend (edu-cloud)\n\n```\nsrc/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/\n├── __init__.py                    — 空（module marker）\n├── models.py                      — ConceptGraphNode + ConceptGraphEdge + EditSyncFailure ORM\n├── schemas.py                     — Pydantic 请求/响应模型\n├── service.py                     — 图谱查询、掌握度聚合、编辑操作、回写 knowledge.db\n└── router.py                      — 3 个端点\n\nsrc/edu_cloud/ai/tools/knowledge_tree.py  — edit_knowledge_graph Agent 工具\n\nalembic/versions/xxxx_add_knowledge_tree_tables.py  — migration\n\nscripts/sync_concept_graph.py      — knowledge.db → PostgreSQL 投影同步\n```\n\n### Frontend (edu-cloud)\n\n```\nfrontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js           — API 调用封装\nfrontend/src/pages/KnowledgeTreePage.vue    — 页面入口 + 布局\nfrontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/\n├── TreeNavPanel.vue                        — 左侧树形导航\n├── ModuleCards.vue                         — 家长入口（模块卡片）\n├── GraphPanel.vue                          — G6 画布封装\n├── NodeDetailDrawer.vue                    — 节点详情抽屉\n├── AgentChatPanel.vue                      — Agent 对话浮窗\n└── useKnowledgeTree.js                     — 组合式函数\n```\n\n### Tests\n\n```\ntests/test_knowledge_tree/\n├── __init__.py\n├── test_models.py           — ORM 字段验证\n├── test_service.py          — 业务逻辑（聚合、编辑）\n├── test_router.py           — API 端点集成测试\n└── test_sync.py             — 投影同步测试\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 1: 数据模型 + Migration\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/__init__.py`\n- Create: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/models.py`\n- Create: `alembic/versions/xxxx_add_knowledge_tree_tables.py`\n- Create: `tests/test_knowledge_tree/__init__.py`\n- Create: `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_models.py`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Write model field tests**\n\n```python\n# tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_models.py\nimport pytest\nfrom sqlalchemy import inspect\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\n\n\ndef test_concept_graph_node_fields():\n    cols = {c.name for c in inspect(ConceptGraphNode).columns}\n    assert \"id\" in cols\n    assert \"name\" in cols\n    assert \"knowledge_level\" in cols\n    assert \"primary_module\" in cols\n    assert \"description\" in cols\n    assert \"synced_at\" in cols\n\n\ndef test_concept_graph_node_tablename():\n    assert ConceptGraphNode.__tablename__ == \"concept_graph_nodes\"\n\n\ndef test_concept_graph_edge_fields():\n    cols = {c.name for c in inspect(ConceptGraphEdge).columns}\n    assert \"id\" in cols\n    assert \"source_id\" in cols\n    assert \"target_id\" in cols\n    assert \"relation_type\" in cols\n    assert \"strength\" in cols\n    assert \"confidence\" in cols\n    assert \"synced_at\" in cols\n\n\ndef test_concept_graph_edge_tablename():\n    assert ConceptGraphEdge.__tablename__ == \"concept_graph_edges\"\n\n\ndef test_concept_graph_edge_unique_constraint():\n    constraints = ConceptGraphEdge.__table_args__\n    unique_cols = None\n    for c in constraints:\n        if hasattr(c, \"columns\"):\n            unique_cols = {col.name for col in c.columns}\n    assert unique_cols == {\"source_id\", \"target_id\", \"relation_type\"}\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Run tests to verify they fail**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_models.py -v`\nExpected: FAIL with `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree'`\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Create module and models**\n\n```python\n# src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/__init__.py\n# (empty)\n```\n\n```python\n# src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/models.py\n\"\"\"知识树图谱 — 投影自 knowledge.db 的概念和关系。\"\"\"\n\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nfrom sqlalchemy import String, Float, Integer, DateTime, Text, ForeignKey, UniqueConstraint\nfrom sqlalchemy.orm import Mapped, mapped_column\n\nfrom edu_cloud.models.base import Base\n\n\nclass ConceptGraphNode(Base):\n    \"\"\"概念图谱节点（投影自 knowledge.db concepts）\"\"\"\n    __tablename__ = \"concept_graph_nodes\"\n\n    id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(64), primary_key=True)\n    name: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(200), nullable=False)\n    knowledge_level: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(4), nullable=False)\n    primary_module: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(10), nullable=False, index=True)\n    description: Mapped[str | None] = mapped_column(Text)\n    synced_at: Mapped[datetime] = mapped_column(DateTime, nullable=False)\n\n\nclass ConceptGraphEdge(Base):\n    \"\"\"概念图谱边（投影自 knowledge.db concept_relations）\"\"\"\n    __tablename__ = \"concept_graph_edges\"\n    __table_args__ = (\n        UniqueConstraint(\"source_id\", \"target_id\", \"relation_type\"),\n    )\n\n    id: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(Integer, primary_key=True, autoincrement=True)\n    source_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(\n        String(64), ForeignKey(\"concept_graph_nodes.id\"), nullable=False, index=True\n    )\n    target_id: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(\n        String(64), ForeignKey(\"concept_graph_nodes.id\"), nullable=False, index=True\n    )\n    relation_type: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(String(30), nullable=False)\n    strength: Mapped[float] = mapped_column(Float, default=1.0)\n    confidence: Mapped[float] = mapped_column(Float, default=1.0)\n    synced_at: Mapped[datetime] = mapped_column(DateTime, nullable=False)\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Run tests to verify they pass**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_models.py -v`\nExpected: 5 passed\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: Generate Alembic migration**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && alembic revision --autogenerate -m \"add knowledge tree tables\"`\nVerify: New file in `alembic/versions/` with `create_table('concept_graph_nodes', ...)` and `create_table('concept_graph_edges', ...)`\n\n- [ ] **Step 6: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/ tests/test_knowledge_tree/ alembic/versions/*knowledge_tree*\ngit commit -m \"feat(knowledge-tree): data models + migration\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ ConceptGraphNode 字段与 design.md §1 一致\n- ✓ ConceptGraphEdge 有 (source_id, target_id, relation_type) 唯一约束\n- ✓ ForeignKey 引用 concept_graph_nodes.id\n- ✗ 不存在 concept_graph_nodes 表但 edge 引用了 node → 需要先建 node 表\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 空表（零节点零边）→ 期望: migration 成功，查询返回空\n- id 最大长度 64 字符 → 期望: `BIO_SR_CP_M5_XXXXX` 格式 ID 不超限\n- 重复边插入 → 期望: UniqueConstraint 拒绝\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: 投影同步脚本\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `scripts/sync_concept_graph.py`\n- Create: `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync.py`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Write sync tests**\n\n```python\n# tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync.py\nimport pytest\nimport sqlite3\nimport tempfile\nimport os\nfrom unittest.mock import AsyncMock, patch, MagicMock\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\n\n\ndef _create_knowledge_db(path):\n    \"\"\"创建测试用的 knowledge.db\"\"\"\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(path)\n    conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        CREATE TABLE concepts (\n            id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n            name TEXT NOT NULL,\n            knowledge_level TEXT NOT NULL,\n            description TEXT,\n            source_block_id TEXT\n        )\n    \"\"\")\n    conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        CREATE TABLE concept_relations (\n            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,\n            source_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n            target_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n            relation_type TEXT NOT NULL,\n            confidence REAL DEFAULT 1.0,\n            strength REAL DEFAULT 1.0\n        )\n    \"\"\")\n    conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        INSERT INTO concepts VALUES\n        ('BIO_SR_CP_M1_ATP', 'ATP与细胞能量货币', 'L1', '描述', NULL)\n    \"\"\")\n    conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        INSERT INTO concepts VALUES\n        ('BIO_SR_CP_M1_CELL_RESP', '细胞呼吸', 'L1', NULL, NULL)\n    \"\"\")\n    conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        INSERT INTO concept_relations VALUES\n        (1, 'BIO_SR_CP_M1_ATP', 'BIO_SR_CP_M1_CELL_RESP', 'prerequisite_hard', 1.0, 1.0)\n    \"\"\")\n    conn.commit()\n    conn.close()\n    return path\n\n\n@pytest.fixture\ndef knowledge_db_path(tmp_path):\n    return _create_knowledge_db(str(tmp_path / \"knowledge.db\"))\n\n\ndef test_read_concepts_from_knowledge_db(knowledge_db_path):\n    from scripts.sync_concept_graph import read_knowledge_db\n    nodes, edges = read_knowledge_db(knowledge_db_path)\n    assert len(nodes) == 2\n    assert nodes[0][\"id\"] == \"BIO_SR_CP_M1_ATP\"\n    assert nodes[0][\"name\"] == \"ATP与细胞能量货币\"\n    assert nodes[0][\"knowledge_level\"] == \"L1\"\n\n\ndef test_read_edges_from_knowledge_db(knowledge_db_path):\n    from scripts.sync_concept_graph import read_knowledge_db\n    nodes, edges = read_knowledge_db(knowledge_db_path)\n    assert len(edges) == 1\n    assert edges[0][\"source_id\"] == \"BIO_SR_CP_M1_ATP\"\n    assert edges[0][\"target_id\"] == \"BIO_SR_CP_M1_CELL_RESP\"\n    assert edges[0][\"relation_type\"] == \"prerequisite_hard\"\n\n\ndef test_extract_module_from_id():\n    from scripts.sync_concept_graph import extract_module\n    assert extract_module(\"BIO_SR_CP_M1_ATP\") == \"M1\"\n    assert extract_module(\"BIO_SR_CP_M2_DNA\") == \"M2\"\n    assert extract_module(\"UNKNOWN_FORMAT\") == \"unknown\"\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_writes_to_db(db, knowledge_db_path):\n    from scripts.sync_concept_graph import read_knowledge_db, sync_to_postgres\n    nodes, edges = read_knowledge_db(knowledge_db_path)\n    await sync_to_postgres(db, nodes, edges)\n\n    from sqlalchemy import select, func\n    node_count = await db.scalar(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))\n    edge_count = await db.scalar(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphEdge))\n    assert node_count == 2\n    assert edge_count == 1\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_is_idempotent(db, knowledge_db_path):\n    from scripts.sync_concept_graph import read_knowledge_db, sync_to_postgres\n    nodes, edges = read_knowledge_db(knowledge_db_path)\n    await sync_to_postgres(db, nodes, edges)\n    await sync_to_postgres(db, nodes, edges)  # 再次同步\n\n    from sqlalchemy import select, func\n    node_count = await db.scalar(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))\n    assert node_count == 2  # 不会翻倍\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Run tests to verify they fail**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync.py -v`\nExpected: FAIL with `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'scripts.sync_concept_graph'`\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Implement sync script**\n\n```python\n# scripts/sync_concept_graph.py\n\"\"\"knowledge.db → PostgreSQL 概念图谱投影同步脚本。\n\n用法:\n    python scripts/sync_concept_graph.py [--knowledge-db PATH]\n\n默认 knowledge.db 路径: ~/edu-knowledge-base/knowledge.db\n\"\"\"\n\nimport argparse\nimport re\nimport sqlite3\nimport sys\nimport asyncio\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nimport sqlalchemy as sa\nfrom sqlalchemy.ext.asyncio import create_async_engine, async_sessionmaker, AsyncSession\n\n# 添加 src 到 path\nsys.path.insert(0, str(Path(__file__).resolve().parent.parent / \"src\"))\n\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\n\n\nDEFAULT_KNOWLEDGE_DB = Path.home() / \"edu-knowledge-base\" / \"knowledge.db\"\n\n_MODULE_RE = re.compile(r\"_M(\\d+)_\")\n\n\ndef extract_module(concept_id: str) -> str:\n    \"\"\"从概念 ID 提取模块编号。e.g. BIO_SR_CP_M1_ATP → M1\"\"\"\n    m = _MODULE_RE.search(concept_id)\n    return f\"M{m.group(1)}\" if m else \"unknown\"\n\n\ndef read_knowledge_db(db_path: str) -> tuple[list[dict], list[dict]]:\n    \"\"\"读取 knowledge.db 的 concepts 和 concept_relations。\"\"\"\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(db_path)\n    conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n\n    nodes = []\n    for row in conn.execute(\"SELECT id, name, knowledge_level, description FROM concepts\"):\n        nodes.append({\n            \"id\": row[\"id\"],\n            \"name\": row[\"name\"],\n            \"knowledge_level\": row[\"knowledge_level\"],\n            \"primary_module\": extract_module(row[\"id\"]),\n            \"description\": row[\"description\"],\n        })\n\n    edges = []\n    for row in conn.execute(\n        \"SELECT source_id, target_id, relation_type, strength, confidence FROM concept_relations\"\n    ):\n        edges.append({\n            \"source_id\": row[\"source_id\"],\n            \"target_id\": row[\"target_id\"],\n            \"relation_type\": row[\"relation_type\"],\n            \"strength\": row[\"strength\"] or 1.0,\n            \"confidence\": row[\"confidence\"] or 1.0,\n        })\n\n    conn.close()\n    return nodes, edges\n\n\nasync def sync_to_postgres(db: AsyncSession, nodes: list[dict], edges: list[dict]):\n    \"\"\"全量替换 PostgreSQL 中的概念图谱数据。\"\"\"\n    now = datetime.now()\n\n    # 先删边再删节点（FK 约束）\n    await db.execute(sa.delete(ConceptGraphEdge))\n    await db.execute(sa.delete(ConceptGraphNode))\n\n    # 插入节点\n    for n in nodes:\n        db.add(ConceptGraphNode(\n            id=n[\"id\"],\n            name=n[\"name\"],\n            knowledge_level=n[\"knowledge_level\"],\n            primary_module=n[\"primary_module\"],\n            description=n[\"description\"],\n            synced_at=now,\n        ))\n\n    await db.flush()\n\n    # 插入边\n    for e in edges:\n        db.add(ConceptGraphEdge(\n            source_id=e[\"source_id\"],\n            target_id=e[\"target_id\"],\n            relation_type=e[\"relation_type\"],\n            strength=e[\"strength\"],\n            confidence=e[\"confidence\"],\n            synced_at=now,\n        ))\n\n    await db.commit()\n\n\nasync def main(knowledge_db_path: str, database_url: str):\n    \"\"\"CLI 入口。\"\"\"\n    print(f\"Reading from {knowledge_db_path} ...\")\n    nodes, edges = read_knowledge_db(knowledge_db_path)\n    print(f\"  {len(nodes)} nodes, {len(edges)} edges\")\n\n    engine = create_async_engine(database_url)\n    session_factory = async_sessionmaker(engine, class_=AsyncSession, expire_on_commit=False)\n\n    async with session_factory() as db:\n        await sync_to_postgres(db, nodes, edges)\n\n    await engine.dispose()\n    print(\"Sync complete.\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"Sync knowledge graph to PostgreSQL\")\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--knowledge-db\",\n        default=str(DEFAULT_KNOWLEDGE_DB),\n        help=\"Path to knowledge.db\",\n    )\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--database-url\",\n        default=\"postgresql+asyncpg://localhost/edu_cloud\",\n        help=\"PostgreSQL connection URL\",\n    )\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n    asyncio.run(main(args.knowledge_db, args.database_url))\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Run tests to verify they pass**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync.py -v`\nExpected: 5 passed\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add scripts/sync_concept_graph.py tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync.py\ngit commit -m \"feat(knowledge-tree): concept graph sync script\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ read_knowledge_db 读取 concepts + concept_relations 两张表\n- ✓ extract_module 从 ID 正则提取模块号\n- ✓ sync_to_postgres 先删后插（全量替换）\n- ✓ 同步幂等（多次执行结果一致）\n- ✗ knowledge.db 不存在时抛出有意义的错误而非 sqlite3 异常\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 空 knowledge.db（零概念零关系）→ 期望: 同步成功，PostgreSQL 表为空\n- ID 不含 _M{N}_ 格式 → 期望: extract_module 返回 \"unknown\"\n- 重复同步 → 期望: 数据不翻倍，node_count 不变\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. 读取概念节点\n   - 入口: `python scripts/sync_concept_graph.py --knowledge-db {path}` (CLI 入口)\n   - 反例: 错误实现会遗漏 description 字段或 knowledge_level\n   - 边界: 空数据库 / 含 NULL description\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync.py::test_read_concepts_from_knowledge_db -v`\n2. 同步幂等性\n   - 入口: `python scripts/sync_concept_graph.py --knowledge-db {path}` 连续执行两次\n   - 反例: 错误实现会 INSERT 而非 TRUNCATE+INSERT，导致数据翻倍\n   - 边界: 同步后再同步\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync.py::test_sync_is_idempotent -v`\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Schemas + Service 层（图谱查询 + 掌握度聚合）\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/schemas.py`\n- Create: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py`\n- Create: `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Write service tests**\n\n```python\n# tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py\nimport pytest\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nfrom sqlalchemy import select\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import StudentDaMastery, DaKnowledgePointMap\n\n\nasync def _seed_graph(db):\n    \"\"\"插入测试图谱数据。\"\"\"\n    now = datetime.now()\n    db.add_all([\n        ConceptGraphNode(id=\"CP_M1_A\", name=\"概念A\", knowledge_level=\"L1\",\n                         primary_module=\"M1\", synced_at=now),\n        ConceptGraphNode(id=\"CP_M1_B\", name=\"概念B\", knowledge_level=\"L1\",\n                         primary_module=\"M1\", synced_at=now),\n        ConceptGraphNode(id=\"CP_M2_C\", name=\"概念C\", knowledge_level=\"L1\",\n                         primary_module=\"M2\", synced_at=now),\n    ])\n    await db.flush()\n    db.add_all([\n        ConceptGraphEdge(source_id=\"CP_M1_A\", target_id=\"CP_M1_B\",\n                         relation_type=\"prerequisite_hard\", synced_at=now),\n        ConceptGraphEdge(source_id=\"CP_M1_B\", target_id=\"CP_M2_C\",\n                         relation_type=\"bridge_to\", synced_at=now),\n    ])\n    await db.commit()\n\n\nasync def _seed_mastery(db):\n    \"\"\"插入测试掌握度数据。\"\"\"\n    db.add_all([\n        DaKnowledgePointMap(da_id=\"DA_001\", knowledge_point_id=\"CP_M1_A\", weight=1.0),\n        DaKnowledgePointMap(da_id=\"DA_002\", knowledge_point_id=\"CP_M1_A\", weight=1.0),\n        DaKnowledgePointMap(da_id=\"DA_003\", knowledge_point_id=\"CP_M1_B\", weight=1.0),\n    ])\n    await db.flush()\n    db.add_all([\n        StudentDaMastery(id=\"m1\", student_id=\"S001\", da_id=\"DA_001\",\n                         mastery_prob=0.9, attempt_count=10, correct_count=9, school_id=\"SCH1\"),\n        StudentDaMastery(id=\"m2\", student_id=\"S001\", da_id=\"DA_002\",\n                         mastery_prob=0.6, attempt_count=5, correct_count=3, school_id=\"SCH1\"),\n        StudentDaMastery(id=\"m3\", student_id=\"S001\", da_id=\"DA_003\",\n                         mastery_prob=0.2, attempt_count=3, correct_count=0, school_id=\"SCH1\"),\n    ])\n    await db.commit()\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_get_graph_all_modules(db):\n    await _seed_graph(db)\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.service import get_graph\n    result = await get_graph(db, module=\"all\")\n    assert len(result[\"nodes\"]) == 3\n    assert len(result[\"edges\"]) == 2\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_get_graph_filter_by_module(db):\n    await _seed_graph(db)\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.service import get_graph\n    result = await get_graph(db, module=\"M1\")\n    assert len(result[\"nodes\"]) == 2\n    assert all(n[\"module\"] == \"M1\" for n in result[\"nodes\"])\n    # 跨模块边 CP_M1_B→CP_M2_C 不应返回（induced subgraph）\n    edge_targets = {e[\"target\"] for e in result[\"edges\"]}\n    assert \"CP_M2_C\" not in edge_targets\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_get_mastery(db):\n    await _seed_graph(db)\n    await _seed_mastery(db)\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.service import get_mastery\n    result = await get_mastery(db, student_id=\"S001\", module=\"all\")\n    assert len(result[\"concept_mastery\"]) >= 1\n    # CP_M1_A 关联 DA_001(0.9) + DA_002(0.6)，平均 0.75\n    cp_a = next(c for c in result[\"concept_mastery\"] if c[\"concept_id\"] == \"CP_M1_A\")\n    assert abs(cp_a[\"mastery\"] - 0.75) < 0.01\n    assert cp_a[\"state\"] == \"fragile\"  # 0.6 <= 0.75 < 0.85\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_get_mastery_unseen_concept(db):\n    await _seed_graph(db)\n    # 不插入 mastery 数据\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.service import get_mastery\n    result = await get_mastery(db, student_id=\"S001\", module=\"all\")\n    for cm in result[\"concept_mastery\"]:\n        assert cm[\"state\"] == \"unseen\"\n        assert cm[\"mastery\"] == 0.0\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_get_mastery_module_aggregation(db):\n    await _seed_graph(db)\n    await _seed_mastery(db)\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.service import get_mastery\n    result = await get_mastery(db, student_id=\"S001\", module=\"all\")\n    assert len(result[\"module_mastery\"]) >= 1\n    m1 = next(m for m in result[\"module_mastery\"] if m[\"module\"] == \"M1\")\n    assert m1[\"mastery\"] > 0\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Run tests to verify they fail**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py -v`\nExpected: FAIL with `ModuleNotFoundError`\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Implement schemas**\n\n```python\n# src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/schemas.py\n\"\"\"知识树 API 请求/响应模型。\"\"\"\n\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\n\n\nclass GraphNodeResponse(BaseModel):\n    id: str\n    name: str\n    level: str\n    module: str\n\n\nclass GraphEdgeResponse(BaseModel):\n    source: str\n    target: str\n    type: str\n    strength: float\n\n\nclass GraphResponse(BaseModel):\n    nodes: list[GraphNodeResponse]\n    edges: list[GraphEdgeResponse]\n\n\nclass ConceptMasteryItem(BaseModel):\n    concept_id: str\n    mastery: float\n    state: str  # solid/fragile/weak/unseen\n    da_count: int\n\n\nclass ModuleMasteryItem(BaseModel):\n    module: str\n    mastery: float\n\n\nclass MasteryResponse(BaseModel):\n    student_id: str\n    concept_mastery: list[ConceptMasteryItem]\n    module_mastery: list[ModuleMasteryItem]\n\n\nclass EditOperation(BaseModel):\n    op: str  # add_node/remove_node/update_node/add_edge/remove_edge/update_edge\n    id: str | None = None\n    source: str | None = None\n    target: str | None = None\n    type: str | None = None\n    name: str | None = None\n    level: str | None = None\n    module: str | None = None\n    description: str | None = None\n    strength: float | None = None\n    fields: dict | None = None\n\n\nclass EditRequest(BaseModel):\n    operations: list[EditOperation]\n\n\nclass EditResponse(BaseModel):\n    success: bool\n    applied: int\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Implement service**\n\n```python\n# src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py\n\"\"\"知识树业务逻辑：图谱查询、掌握度聚合、编辑操作。\"\"\"\n\nimport logging\nfrom collections import defaultdict\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nimport sqlalchemy as sa\nfrom sqlalchemy.ext.asyncio import AsyncSession\n\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import StudentDaMastery, DaKnowledgePointMap\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\n# BKT 4 态分类阈值（与 bkt_engine.py 一致）\n_SOLID = 0.85\n_FRAGILE = 0.6\n_WEAK = 0.3\n\n\ndef _classify_state(mastery: float) -> str:\n    if mastery >= _SOLID:\n        return \"solid\"\n    if mastery >= _FRAGILE:\n        return \"fragile\"\n    if mastery >= _WEAK:\n        return \"weak\"\n    return \"unseen\"\n\n\nasync def get_graph(db: AsyncSession, module: str = \"all\") -> dict:\n    \"\"\"查询图谱结构。\"\"\"\n    node_q = sa.select(ConceptGraphNode)\n    edge_q = sa.select(ConceptGraphEdge)\n\n    if module != \"all\":\n        node_q = node_q.where(ConceptGraphNode.primary_module == module)\n        # 边：source 或 target 在该模块的节点中\n        subq = sa.select(ConceptGraphNode.id).where(ConceptGraphNode.primary_module == module)\n        edge_q = edge_q.where(\n            ConceptGraphEdge.source_id.in_(subq),\n            ConceptGraphEdge.target_id.in_(subq),\n        )\n\n    nodes_result = await db.execute(node_q)\n    edges_result = await db.execute(edge_q)\n\n    nodes = [\n        {\"id\": n.id, \"name\": n.name, \"level\": n.knowledge_level, \"module\": n.primary_module}\n        for n in nodes_result.scalars()\n    ]\n    edges = [\n        {\"source\": e.source_id, \"target\": e.target_id, \"type\": e.relation_type,\n         \"strength\": e.strength}\n        for e in edges_result.scalars()\n    ]\n\n    return {\"nodes\": nodes, \"edges\": edges}\n\n\nasync def get_mastery(db: AsyncSession, student_id: str, module: str = \"all\", school_id: str | None = None) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"查询学生掌握度，聚合到概念和模块级别。\"\"\"\n    # 1. 获取所有概念节点\n    node_q = sa.select(ConceptGraphNode)\n    if module != \"all\":\n        node_q = node_q.where(ConceptGraphNode.primary_module == module)\n    nodes_result = await db.execute(node_q)\n    nodes = list(nodes_result.scalars())\n\n    if not nodes:\n        return {\"student_id\": student_id, \"concept_mastery\": [], \"module_mastery\": []}\n\n    node_ids = [n.id for n in nodes]\n\n    # 2. 获取概念→DA 映射\n    map_q = sa.select(DaKnowledgePointMap).where(\n        DaKnowledgePointMap.knowledge_point_id.in_(node_ids)\n    )\n    maps_result = await db.execute(map_q)\n    maps = list(maps_result.scalars())\n\n    # concept_id → [da_id, ...]\n    concept_das = defaultdict(list)\n    for m in maps:\n        concept_das[m.knowledge_point_id].append(m.da_id)\n\n    # 3. 获取学生的 DA 掌握度\n    all_da_ids = [da for das in concept_das.values() for da in das]\n    mastery_map = {}\n    if all_da_ids:\n        mastery_q = sa.select(StudentDaMastery).where(\n            StudentDaMastery.student_id == student_id,\n            StudentDaMastery.da_id.in_(all_da_ids),\n        )\n        if school_id:\n            mastery_q = mastery_q.where(StudentDaMastery.school_id == school_id)\n        mastery_result = await db.execute(mastery_q)\n        for m in mastery_result.scalars():\n            mastery_map[m.da_id] = m.mastery_prob\n\n    # 4. 聚合到概念级别\n    concept_mastery = []\n    module_scores = defaultdict(list)\n\n    for node in nodes:\n        das = concept_das.get(node.id, [])\n        if not das:\n            concept_mastery.append({\n                \"concept_id\": node.id,\n                \"mastery\": 0.0,\n                \"state\": \"unseen\",\n                \"da_count\": 0,\n            })\n            module_scores[node.primary_module].append(0.0)\n            continue\n\n        da_masteries = [mastery_map.get(da_id, 0.0) for da_id in das]\n        avg_mastery = sum(da_masteries) / len(da_masteries)\n        concept_mastery.append({\n            \"concept_id\": node.id,\n            \"mastery\": round(avg_mastery, 4),\n            \"state\": _classify_state(avg_mastery),\n            \"da_count\": len(das),\n        })\n        module_scores[node.primary_module].append(avg_mastery)\n\n    # 5. 聚合到模块级别\n    module_mastery = []\n    for mod, scores in sorted(module_scores.items()):\n        avg = sum(scores) / len(scores) if scores else 0.0\n        module_mastery.append({\"module\": mod, \"mastery\": round(avg, 4)})\n\n    return {\n        \"student_id\": student_id,\n        \"concept_mastery\": concept_mastery,\n        \"module_mastery\": module_mastery,\n    }\n\n\nasync def apply_edits(db: AsyncSession, operations: list[dict]) -> int:\n    \"\"\"执行编辑操作，返回成功数量。\"\"\"\n    now = datetime.now()\n    applied = 0\n\n    for op_data in operations:\n        op = op_data[\"op\"]\n\n        if op == \"add_node\":\n            db.add(ConceptGraphNode(\n                id=op_data[\"id\"],\n                name=op_data[\"name\"],\n                knowledge_level=op_data.get(\"level\", \"L1\"),\n                primary_module=op_data.get(\"module\", \"unknown\"),\n                description=op_data.get(\"description\"),\n                synced_at=now,\n            ))\n            applied += 1\n\n        elif op == \"remove_node\":\n            # 先删关联边\n            await db.execute(\n                sa.delete(ConceptGraphEdge).where(\n                    sa.or_(\n                        ConceptGraphEdge.source_id == op_data[\"id\"],\n                        ConceptGraphEdge.target_id == op_data[\"id\"],\n                    )\n                )\n            )\n            await db.execute(\n                sa.delete(ConceptGraphNode).where(ConceptGraphNode.id == op_data[\"id\"])\n            )\n            applied += 1\n\n        elif op == \"update_node\":\n            fields = op_data.get(\"fields\", {})\n            if fields:\n                await db.execute(\n                    sa.update(ConceptGraphNode)\n                    .where(ConceptGraphNode.id == op_data[\"id\"])\n                    .values(**fields)\n                )\n                applied += 1\n\n        elif op == \"add_edge\":\n            db.add(ConceptGraphEdge(\n                source_id=op_data[\"source\"],\n                target_id=op_data[\"target\"],\n                relation_type=op_data[\"type\"],\n                strength=op_data.get(\"strength\", 1.0),\n                confidence=1.0,\n                synced_at=now,\n            ))\n            applied += 1\n\n        elif op == \"remove_edge\":\n            await db.execute(\n                sa.delete(ConceptGraphEdge).where(\n                    ConceptGraphEdge.source_id == op_data[\"source\"],\n                    ConceptGraphEdge.target_id == op_data[\"target\"],\n                    ConceptGraphEdge.relation_type == op_data[\"type\"],\n                )\n            )\n            applied += 1\n\n        elif op == \"update_edge\":\n            fields = op_data.get(\"fields\", {})\n            if fields:\n                await db.execute(\n                    sa.update(ConceptGraphEdge)\n                    .where(\n                        ConceptGraphEdge.source_id == op_data[\"source\"],\n                        ConceptGraphEdge.target_id == op_data[\"target\"],\n                        ConceptGraphEdge.relation_type == op_data[\"type\"],\n                    )\n                    .values(**fields)\n                )\n                applied += 1\n\n    await db.commit()\n    return applied\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: Run tests to verify they pass**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py -v`\nExpected: 5 passed\n\n- [ ] **Step 6: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/schemas.py src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py\ngit commit -m \"feat(knowledge-tree): service layer + schemas\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ get_graph 按 module 过滤时返回 induced subgraph（边的 source 和 target 都在该模块内）\n- ✓ get_mastery 聚合 DA → 概念 → 模块三级\n- ✓ _classify_state 阈值与 bkt_engine.py 一致\n- ✓ apply_edits remove_node 级联删除关联边\n- ✗ 不存在的 node id 调用 update_node 不会报错（静默跳过，applied 仍+1）\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 概念无关联 DA → 期望: mastery=0.0, state=\"unseen\"\n- 学生无任何答题记录 → 期望: 所有概念 state=\"unseen\"\n- 空操作列表 → 期望: apply_edits 返回 0\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. 掌握度聚合准确性\n   - 入口: `GET /api/v1/knowledge-tree/mastery?student_id=S001`\n   - 反例: 错误实现会取 MAX 而非 AVG，导致 mastery=0.9 而非 0.75\n   - 边界: 概念关联 0 个 DA / 1 个 DA / 多个 DA\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py::test_get_mastery -v`\n2. 模块过滤返回 induced subgraph\n   - 入口: `GET /api/v1/knowledge-tree/graph?module=M1`\n   - 反例: 错误实现用 OR 查 source/target，会返回跨模块悬空边（CP_M1_B→CP_M2_C）\n   - 边界: 只有一个模块 / 跨模块边 / 边两端都在模块内\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py::test_get_graph_filter_by_module -v`\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: Router（3 个 API 端点）\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py`\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py` — 注册 router\n- Create: `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_router.py`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Write router tests**\n\n```python\n# tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_router.py\nimport pytest\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import StudentDaMastery, DaKnowledgePointMap\n\n\nasync def _seed_data(db):\n    now = datetime.now()\n    db.add_all([\n        ConceptGraphNode(id=\"CP_M1_A\", name=\"概念A\", knowledge_level=\"L1\",\n                         primary_module=\"M1\", synced_at=now),\n        ConceptGraphNode(id=\"CP_M1_B\", name=\"概念B\", knowledge_level=\"L1\",\n                         primary_module=\"M1\", synced_at=now),\n    ])\n    await db.flush()\n    db.add(ConceptGraphEdge(source_id=\"CP_M1_A\", target_id=\"CP_M1_B\",\n                            relation_type=\"prerequisite_hard\", synced_at=now))\n    db.add(DaKnowledgePointMap(da_id=\"DA_001\",\n                               knowledge_point_id=\"CP_M1_A\", weight=1.0))\n    await db.flush()\n    db.add(StudentDaMastery(id=\"m1\", student_id=\"S001\", da_id=\"DA_001\",\n                            mastery_prob=0.8, attempt_count=5, correct_count=4, school_id=\"SCH1\"))\n    await db.commit()\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_get_graph(client, db):\n    await _seed_data(db)\n    resp = await client.get(\"/api/v1/knowledge-tree/graph\")\n    assert resp.status_code == 200\n    data = resp.json()\n    assert len(data[\"nodes\"]) == 2\n    assert len(data[\"edges\"]) == 1\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_get_graph_filter_module(client, db):\n    await _seed_data(db)\n    resp = await client.get(\"/api/v1/knowledge-tree/graph?module=M1\")\n    assert resp.status_code == 200\n    assert len(resp.json()[\"nodes\"]) == 2\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_get_mastery(client, db):\n    await _seed_data(db)\n    resp = await client.get(\"/api/v1/knowledge-tree/mastery?student_id=S001\")\n    assert resp.status_code == 200\n    data = resp.json()\n    assert data[\"student_id\"] == \"S001\"\n    assert len(data[\"concept_mastery\"]) >= 1\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_get_mastery_missing_student_id(client):\n    resp = await client.get(\"/api/v1/knowledge-tree/mastery\")\n    assert resp.status_code == 422  # FastAPI validation error\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_edit_graph(client, db):\n    await _seed_data(db)\n    resp = await client.post(\"/api/v1/knowledge-tree/edit\", json={\n        \"operations\": [\n            {\"op\": \"update_node\", \"id\": \"CP_M1_A\", \"fields\": {\"name\": \"概念A改名\"}}\n        ]\n    })\n    assert resp.status_code == 200\n    assert resp.json()[\"applied\"] == 1\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_graph_requires_auth(unauthenticated_client):\n    resp = await unauthenticated_client.get(\"/api/v1/knowledge-tree/graph\")\n    assert resp.status_code == 401\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_mastery_filters_by_school_id(client, db):\n    \"\"\"掌握度查询按 school_id 过滤，防止跨校数据泄露。\"\"\"\n    await _seed_data(db)\n    # client fixture 绑定 school_id=\"SCH1\"\n    resp = await client.get(\"/api/v1/knowledge-tree/mastery?student_id=S001\")\n    assert resp.status_code == 200\n    data = resp.json()\n    assert data[\"student_id\"] == \"S001\"\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Run tests to verify they fail**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_router.py -v`\nExpected: FAIL\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Implement router**\n\n```python\n# src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py\n\"\"\"知识树 API 端点。\"\"\"\n\nimport logging\nfrom fastapi import APIRouter, Depends, Query\nfrom sqlalchemy.ext.asyncio import AsyncSession\n\nfrom edu_cloud.api.deps import get_db, require_permission\nfrom edu_cloud.core.permissions import Permission\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.schemas import (\n    GraphResponse, MasteryResponse, EditRequest, EditResponse,\n)\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree import service\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\nrouter = APIRouter(prefix=\"/api/v1/knowledge-tree\", tags=[\"knowledge-tree\"])\n\n# NOTE: Permission.VIEW_KNOWLEDGE_TREE 和 EDIT_KNOWLEDGE_TREE 需要在\n# core/permissions.py 的 Permission enum 中新增:\n#   VIEW_KNOWLEDGE_TREE = \"view_knowledge_tree\"\n#   EDIT_KNOWLEDGE_TREE = \"edit_knowledge_tree\"\n# 并在 ROLE_PERMISSIONS 中为相应角色添加这两个权限。\n#\n# NOTE: 在 module_middleware.py 的 ROUTE_MODULE_MAP 中添加:\n#   \"/api/v1/knowledge-tree\": \"research\"\n# 以复用已有的 research 模块治理（与 /api/v1/knowledge 一致）。\n\n\n@router.get(\"/graph\", response_model=GraphResponse)\nasync def get_graph(\n    module: str = Query(\"all\", description=\"模块过滤: M1/M2/M3/M4/M5/all\"),\n    db: AsyncSession = Depends(get_db),\n    current=Depends(require_permission(Permission.VIEW_KNOWLEDGE_TREE)),\n):\n    \"\"\"获取知识图谱结构（节点+边）。\"\"\"\n    return await service.get_graph(db, module=module)\n\n\n@router.get(\"/mastery\", response_model=MasteryResponse)\nasync def get_mastery(\n    student_id: str = Query(..., description=\"学生 ID\"),\n    module: str = Query(\"all\", description=\"模块过滤\"),\n    db: AsyncSession = Depends(get_db),\n    current=Depends(require_permission(Permission.VIEW_KNOWLEDGE_TREE)),\n):\n    \"\"\"获取学生掌握度数据（聚合到概念和模块级别）。\"\"\"\n    school_id = current[\"current_role\"].school_id\n    return await service.get_mastery(db, student_id=student_id, module=module, school_id=school_id)\n\n\n@router.post(\"/edit\", response_model=EditResponse)\nasync def edit_graph(\n    req: EditRequest,\n    db: AsyncSession = Depends(get_db),\n    current=Depends(require_permission(Permission.EDIT_KNOWLEDGE_TREE)),\n):\n    \"\"\"编辑知识图谱（教师/管理员）。\"\"\"\n    operations = [op.model_dump() for op in req.operations]\n    applied = await service.apply_edits(db, operations)\n    logger.info(\"knowledge tree edited: %d operations applied\", applied)\n    return EditResponse(success=True, applied=applied)\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Register router in app.py**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py` 的 router 导入区域添加：\n\n```python\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.router import router as knowledge_tree_router\n```\n\n并在 `for r in [...]` 列表中添加 `knowledge_tree_router`。\n\n- [ ] **Step 4b: Add Permission enum values + ROUTE_MODULE_MAP**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/core/permissions.py` 的 `Permission` enum 中添加：\n\n```python\nVIEW_KNOWLEDGE_TREE = \"view_knowledge_tree\"\nEDIT_KNOWLEDGE_TREE = \"edit_knowledge_tree\"\n```\n\n在 `ROLE_PERMISSIONS` 中为以下角色添加 `Permission.VIEW_KNOWLEDGE_TREE`：\n- `platform_admin`, `district_admin`, `principal`, `academic_director`, `grade_leader`\n- `subject_teacher`, `homeroom_teacher`, `student`, `parent`\n\n为以下角色添加 `Permission.EDIT_KNOWLEDGE_TREE`：\n- `platform_admin`, `district_admin`, `principal`, `subject_teacher`, `homeroom_teacher`\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/middleware/module_middleware.py` 的 `ROUTE_MODULE_MAP` 中添加：\n\n```python\n\"/api/v1/knowledge-tree\": \"research\",\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: Run tests to verify they pass**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_router.py -v`\nExpected: 5 passed\n\n- [ ] **Step 6: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py src/edu_cloud/api/app.py src/edu_cloud/core/permissions.py src/edu_cloud/middleware/module_middleware.py tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_router.py\ngit commit -m \"feat(knowledge-tree): API endpoints + router registration + permissions + module routing\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ GET /graph 默认返回全量，module 参数可过滤\n- ✓ GET /mastery 的 student_id 是必填参数\n- ✓ POST /edit 需要 Permission.EDIT_KNOWLEDGE_TREE（require_permission 工厂依赖）\n- ✓ GET /graph 和 GET /mastery 需要 Permission.VIEW_KNOWLEDGE_TREE\n- ✓ get_mastery 从 current[\"current_role\"].school_id 提取 school_id 过滤，防止跨校查询\n- ✓ Permission enum 需新增 VIEW_KNOWLEDGE_TREE + EDIT_KNOWLEDGE_TREE 并更新 ROLE_PERMISSIONS\n- ✓ ROUTE_MODULE_MAP 需添加 \"/api/v1/knowledge-tree\": \"research\"\n\n**边界条件:**\n- GET /mastery 不传 student_id → 期望: 422 验证错误\n- GET /graph?module=INVALID → 期望: 返回空 nodes/edges\n- POST /edit 空 operations 列表 → 期望: applied=0\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. 图谱查询含认证\n   - 入口: `GET /api/v1/knowledge-tree/graph`（未登录）\n   - 反例: 错误实现未加 get_current_user 依赖，未认证请求返回 200 而非 401\n   - 边界: 未认证 / 已认证无数据 / 已认证有数据\n   - 回归: F002 — 无认证保护\n   - 命令: `pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_router.py::test_graph_requires_auth -v`\n2. 编辑权限保护\n   - 入口: `POST /api/v1/knowledge-tree/edit`（无 knowledge_tree:edit 权限）\n   - 反例: 错误实现未加 require_permission，任意用户可编辑图谱\n   - 边界: 无权限 / 有权限+空操作 / 有权限+有效操作\n   - 回归: F002 — 无权限检查\n   - 命令: `pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_router.py::test_edit_graph -v`\n3. 掌握度按校过滤\n   - 入口: `GET /api/v1/knowledge-tree/mastery?student_id=S001`\n   - 反例: 错误实现不传 school_id，跨校数据泄露\n   - 边界: 同校学生 / 跨校学生（应返回空）\n   - 回归: F002 — 跨校数据泄露\n   - 命令: `pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_router.py::test_mastery_filters_by_school_id -v`\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: Agent 工具\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/knowledge_tree.py`\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/__init__.py` — 添加导入\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Implement Agent tool**\n\n```python\n# src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/knowledge_tree.py\n\"\"\"知识树编辑工具（教师通过 Agent 对话修改知识图谱）。\"\"\"\n\nfrom edu_cloud.ai.registry import tools\nfrom edu_cloud.ai.tool_context import ToolContext, ToolResult\n\n\n@tools.register(\n    name=\"edit_knowledge_graph\",\n    description=(\n        \"编辑知识图谱结构。支持操作：add_node（增加概念）、remove_node（删除概念，级联删边）、\"\n        \"update_node（改名/改描述）、add_edge（加关系）、remove_edge（删关系）、\"\n        \"update_edge（改关系强度）。\"\n        \"概念 ID 格式: BIO_SR_CP_M{N}_{SNAKE_CASE_NAME}。\"\n        \"关系类型: prerequisite_hard（硬前置）/ bridge_to（桥接）/ contrast（对比）。\"\n    ),\n    category=\"L1_knowledge\",\n    module_code=\"research\",  # 复用已有 research 模块（/api/v1/knowledge 已映射到 research）\n    domain=\"knowledge\",\n    allowed_roles=[\"platform_admin\", \"district_admin\", \"principal\", \"subject_teacher\", \"homeroom_teacher\"],\n    risk_level=\"medium\",\n    is_read_only=False,\n    sensitivity=\"school\",\n    parameters={\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n            \"operations\": {\n                \"type\": \"array\",\n                \"description\": \"批量编辑操作列表\",\n                \"items\": {\n                    \"type\": \"object\",\n                    \"properties\": {\n                        \"op\": {\n                            \"type\": \"string\",\n                            \"enum\": [\"add_node\", \"remove_node\", \"update_node\",\n                                     \"add_edge\", \"remove_edge\", \"update_edge\"],\n                        },\n                        \"id\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"节点 ID（node 操作用）\"},\n                        \"name\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"节点名称（add_node 用）\"},\n                        \"level\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"知识层级 L0/L1/L2\"},\n                        \"module\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"模块 M1-M5\"},\n                        \"description\": {\"type\": \"string\"},\n                        \"source\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"边的源节点 ID\"},\n                        \"target\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"边的目标节点 ID\"},\n                        \"type\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"关系类型\"},\n                        \"strength\": {\"type\": \"number\", \"description\": \"关系强度 0-1\"},\n                        \"fields\": {\"type\": \"object\", \"description\": \"update 操作的字段\"},\n                    },\n                    \"required\": [\"op\"],\n                },\n            },\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"operations\"],\n    },\n)\nasync def edit_knowledge_graph(input: dict, ctx: ToolContext) -> ToolResult:\n    try:\n        from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.service import apply_edits\n        operations = input.get(\"operations\", [])\n        if not operations:\n            return ToolResult(success=False, error=\"operations 不能为空\")\n        applied = await apply_edits(ctx.db, operations)\n        return ToolResult(success=True, data={\n            \"message\": f\"成功执行 {applied} 个操作\",\n            \"applied\": applied,\n        })\n    except Exception as e:\n        return ToolResult(success=False, error=str(e))\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Register in __init__.py**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/__init__.py` 末尾添加：\n\n```python\nfrom edu_cloud.ai.tools import knowledge_tree  # noqa: F401\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/knowledge_tree.py src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/__init__.py\ngit commit -m \"feat(knowledge-tree): Agent edit_knowledge_graph tool\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ @tools.register 格式与现有工具一致（exams.py 模式）\n- ✓ allowed_roles 包含 subject_teacher/homeroom_teacher 和管理员（module_code=knowledge 复用已有模块）\n- ✓ 参数 schema 完整定义了 6 种操作类型\n- ✓ ToolResult 显式传 success（设计文档 F002 要求）\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 空 operations 列表 → 期望: 返回 success=False, error=\"operations 不能为空\"\n- 操作中引用不存在的 node id → 期望: apply_edits 静默跳过，不报错\n- 无 ctx.db → 期望: 异常被捕获，返回 ToolResult(success=False)\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. Agent 工具空操作校验\n   - 入口: Agent 调用 `edit_knowledge_graph({\"operations\": []})`\n   - 反例: 错误实现不检查空列表，直接调用 apply_edits 返回 success=True\n   - 边界: 空列表 / None / 缺少 operations key\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py -v`（Agent 工具通过 service 验证）\n2. Agent 工具正常编辑\n   - 入口: Agent 调用 `edit_knowledge_graph({\"operations\": [{\"op\": \"update_node\", ...}]})`\n   - 反例: 错误实现未正确传递 ctx.db，导致数据库操作失败\n   - 边界: 单操作 / 批量操作 / 混合操作类型\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py::test_get_graph_all_modules -v`\n\n---\n\n### Task 6: 编辑回写机制（PostgreSQL → knowledge.db）\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/models.py` — 新增 EditSyncFailure 模型\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py` — 新增 backwrite_to_knowledge_db()\n- Modify: `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py` — 回写测试\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Write backwrite tests**\n\n```python\n# tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py（追加）\nimport tempfile\nimport sqlite3\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_backwrite_to_knowledge_db(db):\n    \"\"\"编辑后回写到 knowledge.db。\"\"\"\n    await _seed_graph(db)\n    # 创建临时 knowledge.db\n    with tempfile.NamedTemporaryFile(suffix=\".db\", delete=False) as f:\n        kb_path = f.name\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(kb_path)\n    conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        CREATE TABLE concepts (\n            id TEXT PRIMARY KEY, name TEXT, knowledge_level TEXT,\n            description TEXT, source_block_id TEXT\n        )\n    \"\"\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO concepts VALUES ('CP_M1_A', '概念A', 'L1', NULL, NULL)\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO concepts VALUES ('CP_M1_B', '概念B', 'L1', NULL, NULL)\")\n    conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        CREATE TABLE concept_relations (\n            source_id TEXT, target_id TEXT, relation_type TEXT,\n            strength REAL DEFAULT 1.0, confidence REAL DEFAULT 1.0,\n            PRIMARY KEY (source_id, target_id)\n        )\n    \"\"\")\n    conn.commit()\n    conn.close()\n\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.service import backwrite_to_knowledge_db\n    result = await backwrite_to_knowledge_db(\n        db, kb_path,\n        [\n            {\"op\": \"update_node\", \"id\": \"CP_M1_A\", \"fields\": {\"name\": \"概念A改名\"}},\n            {\"op\": \"add_edge\", \"source_id\": \"CP_M1_A\", \"target_id\": \"CP_M1_B\",\n             \"relation_type\": \"prerequisite_hard\", \"strength\": 0.8},\n        ]\n    )\n    assert result[\"success\"] is True\n\n    # 验证 knowledge.db 已更新\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(kb_path)\n    name = conn.execute(\"SELECT name FROM concepts WHERE id='CP_M1_A'\").fetchone()[0]\n    assert name == \"概念A改名\"\n    # 验证边已写入\n    edge = conn.execute(\"SELECT * FROM concept_relations WHERE source_id='CP_M1_A'\").fetchone()\n    assert edge is not None\n    assert edge[1] == \"CP_M1_B\"  # target_id\n    conn.close()\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_backwrite_failure_recorded(db):\n    \"\"\"回写失败时记录到 edit_sync_failures 表。\"\"\"\n    await _seed_graph(db)\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.service import backwrite_to_knowledge_db\n    # 使用不存在的路径触发失败\n    result = await backwrite_to_knowledge_db(\n        db, \"/nonexistent/knowledge.db\",\n        [{\"op\": \"update_node\", \"id\": \"CP_M1_A\", \"fields\": {\"name\": \"X\"}}]\n    )\n    assert result[\"success\"] is False\n\n    # 验证失败记录已写入\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import EditSyncFailure\n    from sqlalchemy import select, func\n    count = await db.scalar(select(func.count()).select_from(EditSyncFailure))\n    assert count >= 1\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Run tests to verify they fail**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py::test_backwrite_to_knowledge_db tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py::test_backwrite_failure_recorded -v`\nExpected: FAIL with ImportError / NameError\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Add EditSyncFailure model**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/models.py` 末尾追加：\n\n```python\nclass EditSyncFailure(Base):\n    \"\"\"编辑回写失败记录。\"\"\"\n    __tablename__ = \"edit_sync_failures\"\n\n    id: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(Integer, primary_key=True, autoincrement=True)\n    operation_json: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(Text, nullable=False)\n    error_message: Mapped[str] = mapped_column(Text, nullable=False)\n    created_at: Mapped[datetime] = mapped_column(DateTime, nullable=False)\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Implement backwrite_to_knowledge_db**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py` 的 `apply_edits` 函数后追加：\n\n```python\nimport json\nimport sqlite3 as stdlib_sqlite3\n\nasync def backwrite_to_knowledge_db(\n    db: AsyncSession, knowledge_db_path: str, operations: list[dict]\n) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"将编辑操作回写到 knowledge.db（单向同步补偿）。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        conn = stdlib_sqlite3.connect(knowledge_db_path)\n        for op_data in operations:\n            op = op_data[\"op\"]\n            if op == \"update_node\":\n                fields = op_data.get(\"fields\", {})\n                for col, val in fields.items():\n                    conn.execute(\n                        f\"UPDATE concepts SET {col}=? WHERE id=?\",\n                        (val, op_data[\"id\"]),\n                    )\n            elif op == \"add_node\":\n                conn.execute(\n                    \"INSERT OR REPLACE INTO concepts (id, name, knowledge_level, description) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)\",\n                    (op_data[\"id\"], op_data.get(\"name\", \"\"), op_data.get(\"level\", \"L1\"), op_data.get(\"description\")),\n                )\n            elif op == \"remove_node\":\n                conn.execute(\"DELETE FROM concepts WHERE id=?\", (op_data[\"id\"],))\n                conn.execute(\"DELETE FROM concept_relations WHERE source_id=? OR target_id=?\",\n                             (op_data[\"id\"], op_data[\"id\"]))\n            elif op == \"add_edge\":\n                conn.execute(\n                    \"INSERT OR REPLACE INTO concept_relations (source_id, target_id, relation_type, strength, confidence) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?)\",\n                    (op_data[\"source\"], op_data[\"target\"], op_data.get(\"type\", \"prerequisite_hard\"),\n                     op_data.get(\"strength\", 1.0), op_data.get(\"confidence\", 1.0)),\n                )\n            elif op == \"remove_edge\":\n                conn.execute(\n                    \"DELETE FROM concept_relations WHERE source_id=? AND target_id=? AND relation_type=?\",\n                    (op_data[\"source\"], op_data[\"target\"], op_data[\"type\"]),\n                )\n            elif op == \"update_edge\":\n                fields = op_data.get(\"fields\", {})\n                for col, val in fields.items():\n                    conn.execute(\n                        f\"UPDATE concept_relations SET {col}=? WHERE source_id=? AND target_id=? AND relation_type=?\",\n                        (val, op_data[\"source\"], op_data[\"target\"], op_data[\"type\"]),\n                    )\n        conn.commit()\n        conn.close()\n        logger.info(\"backwrite to knowledge.db succeeded: %d operations\", len(operations))\n        return {\"success\": True, \"synced\": len(operations)}\n    except Exception as e:\n        logger.error(\"backwrite to knowledge.db failed: %s\", e)\n        # 记录失败\n        from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import EditSyncFailure\n        db.add(EditSyncFailure(\n            operation_json=json.dumps(operations, ensure_ascii=False),\n            error_message=str(e),\n            created_at=datetime.now(),\n        ))\n        await db.commit()\n        return {\"success\": False, \"error\": str(e)}\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: Hook backwrite into apply_edits**\n\n在 `apply_edits` 函数的 `await db.commit()` 和 `return applied` 之间添加回写调用：\n\n```python\n    # 回写到 knowledge.db（best-effort，失败不阻塞）\n    import os\n    from pathlib import Path\n    kb_path = os.environ.get(\"KNOWLEDGE_DB_PATH\", str(Path.home() / \"edu-knowledge-base\" / \"knowledge.db\"))\n    if os.path.exists(kb_path):\n        await backwrite_to_knowledge_db(db, kb_path, operations)\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 6: Run tests to verify they pass**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py -v`\nExpected: 全部通过（包含新增的 2 个回写测试）\n\n- [ ] **Step 7: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/models.py src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py\ngit commit -m \"feat(knowledge-tree): backwrite edits to knowledge.db + failure recording\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ backwrite_to_knowledge_db 处理 update_node/add_node/remove_node 三种节点操作\n- ✓ backwrite_to_knowledge_db 处理 add_edge/remove_edge/update_edge 三种边操作\n- ✓ 回写失败时记录到 edit_sync_failures 表，不阻塞主流程\n- ✓ apply_edits 成功后自动触发回写（best-effort）\n\n**边界条件:**\n- knowledge.db 不存在 → 期望: 跳过回写，不报错\n- knowledge.db 被锁定 → 期望: 记录失败到 edit_sync_failures\n- 空 operations 列表 → 期望: 不执行回写\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. 回写成功验证\n   - 入口: `POST /api/v1/knowledge-tree/edit` 后检查 knowledge.db\n   - 反例: 错误实现不调用 backwrite，knowledge.db 数据不变\n   - 边界: update_node / add_node / remove_node / add_edge / remove_edge / update_edge\n   - 回归: F001 — 编辑丢失问题\n   - 命令: `pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py::test_backwrite_to_knowledge_db -v`\n2. 回写失败记录\n   - 入口: `POST /api/v1/knowledge-tree/edit` 指向不存在的 knowledge.db\n   - 反例: 错误实现不记录失败，失败数据永久丢失\n   - 边界: 文件不存在 / 文件被锁定 / 写入权限不足\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py::test_backwrite_failure_recorded -v`\n\n---\n\n### Task 7: 前端 API 模块 + 组合式函数\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js`\n- Create: `frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/useKnowledgeTree.js`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Create API module**\n\n```javascript\n// frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js\nimport client from './client'\n\nexport const getGraph = (module = 'all') =>\n  client.get('/knowledge-tree/graph', { params: { module } })\n\nexport const getMastery = (studentId, module = 'all') =>\n  client.get('/knowledge-tree/mastery', { params: { student_id: studentId, module } })\n\nexport const editGraph = (operations) =>\n  client.post('/knowledge-tree/edit', { operations })\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Create composable**\n\n```javascript\n// frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/useKnowledgeTree.js\nimport { ref, computed } from 'vue'\nimport { getGraph, getMastery, editGraph } from '../../api/knowledgeTree'\n\nexport function useKnowledgeTree() {\n  const graphData = ref({ nodes: [], edges: [] })\n  const masteryData = ref({ student_id: '', concept_mastery: [], module_mastery: [] })\n  const loading = ref(false)\n  const selectedModule = ref('all')\n  const selectedStudentId = ref(null)\n\n  const moduleMastery = computed(() => masteryData.value.module_mastery)\n\n  const nodesWithMastery = computed(() => {\n    const masteryMap = {}\n    for (const cm of masteryData.value.concept_mastery) {\n      masteryMap[cm.concept_id] = cm\n    }\n    return graphData.value.nodes.map(node => ({\n      ...node,\n      mastery: masteryMap[node.id]?.mastery ?? 0,\n      mastery_state: masteryMap[node.id]?.state ?? 'unseen',\n      da_count: masteryMap[node.id]?.da_count ?? 0,\n    }))\n  })\n\n  async function loadGraph(module = 'all') {\n    selectedModule.value = module\n    const resp = await getGraph(module)\n    graphData.value = resp.data\n  }\n\n  async function loadMastery(studentId, module = 'all') {\n    selectedStudentId.value = studentId\n    const resp = await getMastery(studentId, module)\n    masteryData.value = resp.data\n  }\n\n  async function applyEdit(operations) {\n    loading.value = true\n    try {\n      const resp = await editGraph(operations)\n      // 编辑后重新加载图谱\n      await loadGraph(selectedModule.value)\n      return resp.data\n    } finally {\n      loading.value = false\n    }\n  }\n\n  return {\n    graphData,\n    masteryData,\n    loading,\n    selectedModule,\n    selectedStudentId,\n    moduleMastery,\n    nodesWithMastery,\n    loadGraph,\n    loadMastery,\n    applyEdit,\n  }\n}\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/useKnowledgeTree.js\ngit commit -m \"feat(knowledge-tree): frontend API + composable\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ API 路径与后端 router prefix 一致（/knowledge-tree/）\n- ✓ nodesWithMastery 合并图谱节点和掌握度数据\n- ✓ applyEdit 编辑后自动刷新图谱\n\n---\n\n### Task 8: 前端 TreeNavPanel + ModuleCards\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ModuleCards.vue`\n- Create: `frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/TreeNavPanel.vue`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Create ModuleCards（家长入口）**\n\n```vue\n<!-- frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ModuleCards.vue -->\n<template>\n  <div class=\"module-cards\">\n    <div\n      v-for=\"mod in modules\"\n      :key=\"mod.module\"\n      class=\"module-card\"\n      @click=\"$emit('select', mod.module)\"\n    >\n      <div class=\"card-header\">\n        <span class=\"module-name\">{{ moduleNames[mod.module] || mod.module }}</span>\n        <span class=\"mastery-pct\" :style=\"{ color: masteryColor(mod.mastery) }\">\n          {{ mod.mastery > 0 ? Math.round(mod.mastery * 100) + '%' : '--' }}\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <n-progress\n        type=\"circle\"\n        :percentage=\"Math.round(mod.mastery * 100)\"\n        :color=\"masteryColor(mod.mastery)\"\n        :rail-color=\"'rgba(255,255,255,0.1)'\"\n        :stroke-width=\"6\"\n        :show-indicator=\"false\"\n        style=\"width: 80px; height: 80px; margin: 12px auto\"\n      />\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup>\nimport { NProgress } from 'naive-ui'\n\ndefineProps({\n  modules: { type: Array, default: () => [] },\n})\ndefineEmits(['select'])\n\nconst moduleNames = {\n  M1: '分子与细胞',\n  M2: '遗传与进化',\n  M3: '稳态与调节',\n  M4: '生物与环境',\n  M5: '生物技术与工程',\n}\n\nfunction masteryColor(mastery) {\n  if (mastery >= 0.85) return '#22c55e'\n  if (mastery >= 0.6) return '#eab308'\n  if (mastery >= 0.3) return '#ef4444'\n  return '#6b7280'\n}\n</script>\n\n<style scoped>\n.module-cards {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));\n  gap: 12px;\n  padding: 16px;\n}\n.module-card {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  padding: 16px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: background 0.2s;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.module-card:hover {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n}\n.card-header {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n}\n.module-name {\n  font-size: 14px;\n  font-weight: 500;\n}\n.mastery-pct {\n  font-size: 18px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n}\n</style>\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Create TreeNavPanel**\n\n```vue\n<!-- frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/TreeNavPanel.vue -->\n<template>\n  <div class=\"tree-nav-panel\">\n    <div class=\"nav-header\">\n      <slot name=\"student-selector\" />\n    </div>\n    <n-tree\n      :data=\"treeData\"\n      :default-expanded-keys=\"expandedKeys\"\n      :selected-keys=\"selectedKeys\"\n      :render-suffix=\"renderSuffix\"\n      @update:selected-keys=\"handleSelect\"\n      block-line\n    />\n    <div v-if=\"weakConcepts.length\" class=\"weak-section\">\n      <div class=\"section-title\">薄弱概念 Top 5</div>\n      <div v-for=\"c in weakConcepts\" :key=\"c.concept_id\" class=\"weak-item\">\n        <span>{{ c.name }}</span>\n        <span :style=\"{ color: masteryColor(c.mastery) }\">\n          {{ Math.round(c.mastery * 100) }}%\n        </span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup>\nimport { computed, h } from 'vue'\nimport { NTree, NTag } from 'naive-ui'\n\nconst props = defineProps({\n  moduleMastery: { type: Array, default: () => [] },\n  nodesWithMastery: { type: Array, default: () => [] },\n  selectedModule: { type: String, default: 'all' },\n})\nconst emit = defineEmits(['select-module'])\n\nconst moduleNames = {\n  M1: '分子与细胞',\n  M2: '遗传与进化',\n  M3: '稳态与调节',\n  M4: '生物与环境',\n  M5: '生物技术与工程',\n}\n\nfunction masteryColor(mastery) {\n  if (mastery >= 0.85) return '#22c55e'\n  if (mastery >= 0.6) return '#eab308'\n  if (mastery >= 0.3) return '#ef4444'\n  return '#6b7280'\n}\n\nconst treeData = computed(() => {\n  const modules = ['M1', 'M2', 'M3', 'M4', 'M5']\n  return modules.map(mod => {\n    const modMastery = props.moduleMastery.find(m => m.module === mod)\n    const concepts = props.nodesWithMastery.filter(n => n.module === mod)\n    return {\n      key: mod,\n      label: moduleNames[mod] || mod,\n      mastery: modMastery?.mastery ?? 0,\n      children: concepts.map(c => ({\n        key: c.id,\n        label: c.name,\n        mastery: c.mastery,\n        isLeaf: true,\n      })),\n    }\n  })\n})\n\nconst expandedKeys = computed(() =>\n  props.selectedModule !== 'all' ? [props.selectedModule] : []\n)\nconst selectedKeys = computed(() =>\n  props.selectedModule !== 'all' ? [props.selectedModule] : []\n)\n\nconst weakConcepts = computed(() => {\n  return [...props.nodesWithMastery]\n    .filter(n => n.mastery_state === 'weak' || n.mastery_state === 'fragile')\n    .sort((a, b) => a.mastery - b.mastery)\n    .slice(0, 5)\n    .map(n => ({ concept_id: n.id, name: n.name, mastery: n.mastery }))\n})\n\nfunction renderSuffix({ option }) {\n  const m = option.mastery ?? 0\n  if (m === 0) return null\n  return h('span', {\n    style: { color: masteryColor(m), fontSize: '12px', marginLeft: '4px' },\n  }, Math.round(m * 100) + '%')\n}\n\nfunction handleSelect(keys) {\n  if (keys.length > 0) {\n    const key = keys[0]\n    if (['M1', 'M2', 'M3', 'M4', 'M5'].includes(key)) {\n      emit('select-module', key)\n    }\n  }\n}\n</script>\n\n<style scoped>\n.tree-nav-panel {\n  height: 100%;\n  overflow-y: auto;\n  padding: 12px;\n}\n.nav-header {\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\n}\n.weak-section {\n  margin-top: 16px;\n  padding-top: 12px;\n  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n}\n.section-title {\n  font-size: 12px;\n  color: #888;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n.weak-item {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  font-size: 13px;\n  padding: 4px 0;\n}\n</style>\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ModuleCards.vue frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/TreeNavPanel.vue\ngit commit -m \"feat(knowledge-tree): TreeNavPanel + ModuleCards components\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ ModuleCards 五张卡片对应 M1-M5\n- ✓ TreeNavPanel 用 NTree 组件渲染层级\n- ✓ 掌握度百分比显示和颜色映射与 design.md §3 一致\n- ✓ 薄弱概念 Top 5 列表\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 零模块数据（moduleMastery 为空数组）→ 期望: 树形导航显示 M1-M5 骨架，mastery 显示 0%\n- 单模块仅 1 个概念 → 期望: 树节点正常渲染，弱概念列表可能为空\n- 所有概念掌握度 100% → 期望: 弱概念 Top 5 区域为空（无 weak/fragile）\n\n---\n\n### Task 9: 前端 GraphPanel（AntV G6）\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `frontend/package.json` — 添加 @antv/g6\n- Create: `frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/GraphPanel.vue`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Install G6**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud/frontend && npm install @antv/g6@^5`\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Create GraphPanel**\n\n```vue\n<!-- frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/GraphPanel.vue -->\n<template>\n  <div class=\"graph-panel\">\n    <div class=\"toolbar\">\n      <n-button-group size=\"small\">\n        <n-button @click=\"zoomIn\">+</n-button>\n        <n-button @click=\"zoomOut\">-</n-button>\n        <n-button @click=\"fitView\">居中</n-button>\n      </n-button-group>\n      <n-button size=\"small\" quaternary @click=\"toggleLayout\">\n        {{ layoutType === 'force' ? '径向布局' : '力导向' }}\n      </n-button>\n    </div>\n    <div ref=\"containerRef\" class=\"graph-container\" />\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup>\nimport { ref, onMounted, onUnmounted, watch, nextTick } from 'vue'\nimport { NButton, NButtonGroup } from 'naive-ui'\nimport { Graph } from '@antv/g6'\n\nconst props = defineProps({\n  nodes: { type: Array, default: () => [] },\n  edges: { type: Array, default: () => [] },\n  selectedModule: { type: String, default: 'all' },\n})\nconst emit = defineEmits(['node-click'])\n\nconst containerRef = ref(null)\nconst layoutType = ref('force')\nlet graph = null\n\nconst STATE_COLORS = {\n  solid: '#22c55e',\n  fragile: '#eab308',\n  weak: '#ef4444',\n  unseen: '#6b7280',\n}\n\nconst LEVEL_SIZES = { L0: 40, L1: 28, L2: 20 }\n\nconst EDGE_STYLES = {\n  prerequisite_hard: { stroke: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.3)', lineDash: [0], endArrow: true },\n  bridge_to: { stroke: 'rgba(74,158,255,0.3)', lineDash: [4, 3], endArrow: false },\n  contrast: { stroke: 'rgba(234,179,8,0.3)', lineDash: [2, 2], endArrow: false },\n}\n\nfunction buildGraphData() {\n  const nodes = props.nodes.map(n => ({\n    id: n.id,\n    data: {\n      label: n.name.length > 6 ? n.name.slice(0, 6) + '…' : n.name,\n      fullName: n.name,\n      level: n.level,\n      module: n.module,\n      mastery: n.mastery ?? 0,\n      mastery_state: n.mastery_state ?? 'unseen',\n      da_count: n.da_count ?? 0,\n    },\n  }))\n  const edges = props.edges.map((e, i) => ({\n    id: `edge-${i}`,\n    source: e.source,\n    target: e.target,\n    data: { type: e.type, strength: e.strength },\n  }))\n  return { nodes, edges }\n}\n\nfunction createGraph() {\n  if (!containerRef.value) return\n\n  const data = buildGraphData()\n\n  graph = new Graph({\n    container: containerRef.value,\n    data,\n    autoFit: 'view',\n    layout: {\n      type: layoutType.value === 'force' ? 'force' : 'radial',\n      animated: true,\n      clustering: true,\n      nodeClusterBy: 'module',\n    },\n    node: {\n      style: {\n        size: d => LEVEL_SIZES[d.data.level] || 28,\n        fill: d => STATE_COLORS[d.data.mastery_state] || '#6b7280',\n        stroke: d => props.selectedModule !== 'all' && d.data.module !== props.selectedModule\n          ? 'rgba(255,255,255,0.05)' : 'rgba(255,255,255,0.2)',\n        fillOpacity: d => props.selectedModule !== 'all' && d.data.module !== props.selectedModule\n          ? 0.2 : 0.9,\n        labelText: d => d.data.label,\n        labelFill: '#fff',\n        labelFontSize: 10,\n      },\n    },\n    edge: {\n      style: d => {\n        const style = EDGE_STYLES[d.data.type] || EDGE_STYLES.prerequisite_hard\n        return {\n          stroke: style.stroke,\n          lineDash: style.lineDash,\n          endArrow: style.endArrow,\n          lineWidth: 1.5,\n        }\n      },\n    },\n    behaviors: ['drag-canvas', 'zoom-canvas', 'drag-element', 'click-select'],\n  })\n\n  graph.on('node:click', (evt) => {\n    const nodeData = evt.itemData || evt.target?.id\n    if (nodeData) {\n      const node = props.nodes.find(n => n.id === (nodeData.id || nodeData))\n      if (node) emit('node-click', node)\n    }\n  })\n\n  graph.render()\n}\n\nfunction destroyGraph() {\n  if (graph) {\n    graph.destroy()\n    graph = null\n  }\n}\n\nfunction zoomIn() { graph?.zoom(1.2) }\nfunction zoomOut() { graph?.zoom(0.8) }\nfunction fitView() { graph?.fitView() }\n\nfunction toggleLayout() {\n  layoutType.value = layoutType.value === 'force' ? 'radial' : 'force'\n  destroyGraph()\n  nextTick(createGraph)\n}\n\nwatch(() => [props.nodes, props.edges, props.selectedModule], () => {\n  destroyGraph()\n  nextTick(createGraph)\n}, { deep: true })\n\nonMounted(() => nextTick(createGraph))\nonUnmounted(destroyGraph)\n</script>\n\n<style scoped>\n.graph-panel {\n  position: relative;\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n}\n.toolbar {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 8px;\n  right: 8px;\n  z-index: 10;\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 8px;\n}\n.graph-container {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n  min-height: 500px;\n}\n</style>\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add frontend/package.json frontend/package-lock.json frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/GraphPanel.vue\ngit commit -m \"feat(knowledge-tree): G6 GraphPanel component\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 节点大小按 knowledge_level 映射（L0=40, L1=28, L2=20）\n- ✓ 节点颜色按 mastery_state 映射（solid/fragile/weak/unseen）\n- ✓ 边样式按 relation_type 区分（实线/虚线/点线）\n- ✓ 模块过滤时非选中模块节点变暗\n- ✓ 支持力导向/径向布局切换\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 零节点零边（空图谱）→ 期望: 画布渲染空白，不报 JS 错误\n- 1000+ 节点（大图谱）→ 期望: 力导向布局不卡死，渲染完成\n- 切换布局后立即切换回来 → 期望: 不触发竞态条件（destroyGraph 正确清理）\n\n---\n\n### Task 10: 前端 NodeDetailDrawer\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Create NodeDetailDrawer**\n\n```vue\n<!-- frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue -->\n<template>\n  <n-drawer v-model:show=\"visible\" :width=\"360\" placement=\"right\">\n    <n-drawer-content :title=\"node?.name || ''\" closable>\n      <template v-if=\"node\">\n        <n-descriptions :column=\"1\" label-placement=\"left\" size=\"small\">\n          <n-descriptions-item label=\"ID\">\n            <n-text code>{{ node.id }}</n-text>\n          </n-descriptions-item>\n          <n-descriptions-item label=\"层级\">{{ node.level }}</n-descriptions-item>\n          <n-descriptions-item label=\"模块\">{{ node.module }}</n-descriptions-item>\n          <n-descriptions-item label=\"掌握度\">\n            <n-tag :type=\"stateTagType\" size=\"small\">\n              {{ node.mastery_state }} · {{ Math.round((node.mastery ?? 0) * 100) }}%\n            </n-tag>\n          </n-descriptions-item>\n          <n-descriptions-item label=\"DA 数量\">{{ node.da_count ?? 0 }}</n-descriptions-item>\n        </n-descriptions>\n\n        <!-- 教师编辑表单 -->\n        <template v-if=\"canEdit\">\n          <n-divider />\n          <n-form ref=\"formRef\" :model=\"editForm\" size=\"small\">\n            <n-form-item label=\"概念名称\">\n              <n-input v-model:value=\"editForm.name\" />\n            </n-form-item>\n            <n-form-item label=\"描述\">\n              <n-input v-model:value=\"editForm.description\" type=\"textarea\" :rows=\"3\" />\n            </n-form-item>\n            <n-button type=\"primary\" size=\"small\" @click=\"handleSave\" :loading=\"saving\">\n              保存修改\n            </n-button>\n          </n-form>\n        </template>\n      </template>\n    </n-drawer-content>\n  </n-drawer>\n</template>\n\n<script setup>\nimport { ref, computed, watch } from 'vue'\nimport {\n  NDrawer, NDrawerContent, NDescriptions, NDescriptionsItem,\n  NTag, NText, NForm, NFormItem, NInput, NButton, NDivider, useMessage,\n} from 'naive-ui'\n\nconst props = defineProps({\n  node: { type: Object, default: null },\n  canEdit: { type: Boolean, default: false },\n})\nconst emit = defineEmits(['close', 'edit'])\n\nconst visible = defineModel('show', { type: Boolean, default: false })\nconst message = useMessage()\nconst saving = ref(false)\nconst editForm = ref({ name: '', description: '' })\n\nconst stateTagType = computed(() => {\n  const map = { solid: 'success', fragile: 'warning', weak: 'error', unseen: 'default' }\n  return map[props.node?.mastery_state] || 'default'\n})\n\nwatch(() => props.node, (n) => {\n  if (n) {\n    editForm.value = { name: n.name || '', description: n.description || '' }\n  }\n})\n\nasync function handleSave() {\n  if (!props.node) return\n  saving.value = true\n  try {\n    const fields = {}\n    if (editForm.value.name !== props.node.name) fields.name = editForm.value.name\n    if (editForm.value.description !== (props.node.description || '')) {\n      fields.description = editForm.value.description\n    }\n    if (Object.keys(fields).length === 0) {\n      message.info('没有变更')\n      return\n    }\n    emit('edit', [{\n      op: 'update_node',\n      id: props.node.id,\n      fields,\n    }])\n    message.success('已保存')\n  } finally {\n    saving.value = false\n  }\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue\ngit commit -m \"feat(knowledge-tree): NodeDetailDrawer component\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 教师编辑表单通过 canEdit prop 控制显隐\n- ✓ 保存时只发送实际变更的字段\n- ✓ 无变更时提示而非发送空请求\n\n**边界条件:**\n- node 为 null（抽屉关闭状态）→ 期望: 不渲染内容，不报错\n- canEdit=false（家长/学生角色）→ 期望: 编辑表单隐藏，只显示详情\n- 概念名称为空字符串 → 期望: 保存时不发送空字段更新\n\n---\n\n### Task 11: 前端页面组装 + 路由注册\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `frontend/src/pages/KnowledgeTreePage.vue`\n- Modify: `frontend/src/router/index.js` — 添加路由\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Create KnowledgeTreePage**\n\n```vue\n<!-- frontend/src/pages/KnowledgeTreePage.vue -->\n<template>\n  <div class=\"knowledge-tree-page\">\n    <!-- 家长入口：模块卡片（未选择模块时显示） -->\n    <ModuleCards\n      v-if=\"showCards\"\n      :modules=\"moduleMastery\"\n      @select=\"handleModuleSelect\"\n    />\n\n    <!-- 主视图：左侧导航 + 右侧图谱 -->\n    <div v-else class=\"main-layout\">\n      <div class=\"nav-side\" :class=\"{ collapsed: navCollapsed }\">\n        <TreeNavPanel\n          :module-mastery=\"moduleMastery\"\n          :nodes-with-mastery=\"nodesWithMastery\"\n          :selected-module=\"selectedModule\"\n          @select-module=\"handleModuleSelect\"\n        >\n          <template #student-selector>\n            <n-button size=\"small\" quaternary @click=\"backToCards\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8px\">\n              ← 返回模块概览\n            </n-button>\n          </template>\n        </TreeNavPanel>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"graph-side\">\n        <GraphPanel\n          :nodes=\"nodesWithMastery\"\n          :edges=\"graphData.edges\"\n          :selected-module=\"selectedModule\"\n          @node-click=\"handleNodeClick\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 节点详情抽屉 -->\n    <NodeDetailDrawer\n      v-model:show=\"drawerVisible\"\n      :node=\"selectedNode\"\n      :can-edit=\"canEdit\"\n      @edit=\"handleEdit\"\n    />\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup>\nimport { ref, computed, onMounted } from 'vue'\nimport { NButton, useMessage } from 'naive-ui'\nimport { useAuthStore } from '../stores/auth'\nimport { useKnowledgeTree } from '../components/knowledge-tree/useKnowledgeTree'\nimport ModuleCards from '../components/knowledge-tree/ModuleCards.vue'\nimport TreeNavPanel from '../components/knowledge-tree/TreeNavPanel.vue'\nimport GraphPanel from '../components/knowledge-tree/GraphPanel.vue'\nimport NodeDetailDrawer from '../components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue'\n\nconst message = useMessage()\nconst {\n  graphData, loading, selectedModule, moduleMastery,\n  nodesWithMastery, loadGraph, loadMastery, applyEdit,\n} = useKnowledgeTree()\n\nconst showCards = ref(true)\nconst navCollapsed = ref(false)\nconst drawerVisible = ref(false)\nconst selectedNode = ref(null)\nconst selectedStudentId = ref(null)  // 教师角色时通过学生选择器设置\n\nconst authStore = useAuthStore()\n// 使用 checkPermission 方法（与 Permission enum 对齐）\nconst canEdit = computed(() => authStore.checkPermission('edit_knowledge_tree'))\nconst currentSchoolContext = computed(() => authStore.currentContext)\n// 教师/管理员角色需要学生选择器；学生/家长的 studentId 由后端根据当前用户上下文确定\nconst needsStudentSelector = computed(() =>\n  ['subject_teacher', 'homeroom_teacher', 'principal', 'academic_director', 'grade_leader'].includes(authStore.roleName)\n)\n// studentId: 教师角色时从选择器获取，学生/家长角色时由 API 根据 currentContext 自动确定\nconst studentId = computed(() => {\n  // 非教师角色：不传 studentId，后端根据登录用户上下文确定\n  if (!needsStudentSelector.value) return null\n  return selectedStudentId.value  // teacher: from student selector\n})\n\nasync function init() {\n  await loadGraph()\n  await loadMastery(studentId.value)\n}\n\nfunction handleModuleSelect(mod) {\n  showCards.value = false\n  selectedModule.value = mod\n  loadGraph(mod)\n}\n\nfunction backToCards() {\n  showCards.value = true\n  selectedModule.value = 'all'\n  loadGraph('all')\n}\n\nfunction handleNodeClick(node) {\n  selectedNode.value = node\n  drawerVisible.value = true\n}\n\nasync function handleEdit(operations) {\n  try {\n    await applyEdit(operations)\n    message.success('图谱已更新')\n    // 刷新掌握度\n    await loadMastery(studentId.value, selectedModule.value)\n  } catch (e) {\n    message.error('编辑失败: ' + e.message)\n  }\n}\n\nonMounted(init)\n</script>\n\n<style scoped>\n.knowledge-tree-page {\n  height: calc(100vh - 64px);\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n.main-layout {\n  display: flex;\n  height: 100%;\n}\n.nav-side {\n  width: 280px;\n  border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  overflow-y: auto;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n.nav-side.collapsed {\n  width: 0;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n.graph-side {\n  flex: 1;\n  position: relative;\n}\n</style>\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Register route**\n\n在 `frontend/src/router/index.js` 的 children 数组中添加：\n\n```javascript\n{\n  path: 'knowledge-tree',\n  name: 'KnowledgeTree',\n  component: () => import('../pages/KnowledgeTreePage.vue'),\n},\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add frontend/src/pages/KnowledgeTreePage.vue frontend/src/router/index.js\ngit commit -m \"feat(knowledge-tree): KnowledgeTreePage + route registration\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 家长默认看到模块卡片，点击进入图谱\n- ✓ \"返回模块概览\" 按钮\n- ✓ 节点点击打开详情抽屉\n- ✓ 编辑后自动刷新图谱和掌握度\n- ✓ 路由注册为懒加载\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 学生角色登录 → 期望: canEdit=false，编辑表单不显示；studentId 从 authStore 获取\n- 家长角色登录 → 期望: canEdit=false；studentId 取 bound_student_ids[0]\n- 教师角色登录且无绑定学生 → 期望: studentId=null，需选择学生后才加载掌握度\n\n---\n\n## Contract Pack\n\n### Invariants\n\n1. **Induced subgraph**: `GET /graph?module=X` 返回的边的 source 和 target 都在模块 X 的节点集合中，不存在悬空边\n2. **Mastery = weighted avg**: 概念掌握度 = 该概念关联的所有 DA 的 mastery_prob 算术平均值；模块掌握度 = 模块内所有概念掌握度的算术平均值\n3. **Backwrite consistency**: 通过 edit API 成功的 update_node/add_node/remove_node 操作会回写到 knowledge.db；回写失败时记录到 edit_sync_failures 表\n4. **Auth enforcement**: graph/mastery 端点需要登录；edit 端点需要 `knowledge_tree:edit` 权限；mastery 按 school_id 过滤\n\n### Counter-examples\n\n1. **Dangling edge**: 当 module=M1 过滤时，边 CP_M1_B→CP_M2_C（target 不在 M1 中）不应出现在结果中。如果使用 OR 条件查询边，这条跨模块边会被错误返回。\n2. **Edit lost on resync**: 教师通过 Agent 编辑了概念名称，但下次 sync_concept_graph.py 运行时全量替换 PostgreSQL 数据。如果没有 backwrite 机制，编辑内容会在下次同步后丢失。\n\n### Risk Modules\n\n- `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py` — 权限检查、参数校验\n- `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py` — 聚合逻辑、回写逻辑\n- `scripts/sync_concept_graph.py` — 全量同步可能覆盖编辑\n\n### Test Debt\n\n| 项目 | 原因 | 截止日期 |\n|------|------|---------|\n| Agent 工具端到端测试 | 需要 ToolContext mock 基础设施 | MVP+1 迭代 |\n| edge 回写（add_edge/remove_edge）| knowledge.db concept_relations 格式差异 | MVP+1 迭代 |\n| 前端组件视觉测试 | 需要 Playwright/Cypress 基础设施 | MVP+2 迭代 |\n\n---\n\n### Task 12: 全量测试 + 收尾\n\n**Files:**\n- 无新建文件\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Run all backend tests**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/ -v`\nExpected: 所有测试通过（15+ tests）\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Run full test suite**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/ -v --tb=short`\nExpected: 无新增失败（预存在的失败不计）\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Build frontend**\n\nRun: `cd ~/edu-cloud/frontend && npm run build`\nExpected: 构建成功，无错误\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Final commit**\n\n如有未提交的修复，合并提交：\n\n```bash\ngit add -A && git commit -m \"fix(knowledge-tree): final adjustments\"\n```\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 后端测试全绿\n- ✓ 前端构建成功\n- ✓ 无计划外文件变更\n"
    }
