F001  
Severity: HIGH  
Category: code-bug  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: 知识树页在初始化和编辑后刷新时，会无条件请求 `/knowledge-tree/mastery`；对家长角色没有学生来源，对教师/校级角色也没有任何学生选择器可写入 `selectedStudentId`，因此实际请求会带着空 `student_id`。  
After-behavior: 只有在学生上下文已解析时才请求 mastery，或后端真正支持“从当前上下文推导 student_id”的调用路径。  
Evidence: [2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2309](C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2309) [2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2409](C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2409) [KnowledgeTreePage.vue#L70](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/pages/KnowledgeTreePage.vue#L70) [KnowledgeTreePage.vue#L78](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/pages/KnowledgeTreePage.vue#L78) [useKnowledgeTree.js#L32](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/useKnowledgeTree.js#L32) [knowledgeTree.js#L6](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js#L6) [router.py#L31](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py#L31)  
Impact: 当前页面的核心“掌握度可视化”对所有角色都不成立：家长没有绑定学生来源，教师/校级角色也没有选择学生的 UI；首次加载就会打到 422，模块卡片与节点着色都拿不到数据。  
Repair hypothesis: 让页面和 API 在“学生身份解析”上选定单一路径即可，不要同时保留“前端传 null”和“后端必填 student_id”两套互斥约定。

F002  
Severity: HIGH  
Category: code-bug  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: `apply_edits` 只有在 `knowledge.db` 文件存在时才尝试回写；文件不存在时直接返回成功，不回写，也不写 `edit_sync_failures`。  
After-behavior: 成功的编辑主路径必须要么完成回写，要么至少留下失败记录，不能静默跳过。  
Evidence: [2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2421](C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2421) [2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2427](C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2427) [service.py#L225](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py#L225) [test_service.py#L151](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py#L151)  
Impact: 一旦部署环境没挂好 `knowledge.db`，编辑接口仍会返回成功，但修改只落在 PostgreSQL 投影里；下次 `sync_concept_graph.py` 全量同步后会被覆盖，正是 Contract Pack 明确要避免的“edit lost on resync”。我本地按同一路径复现后，`apply_edits` 返回 `applied=1`，`EditSyncFailure` 计数仍为 `0`。  
Repair hypothesis:  
1. likely repair direction: 把“回写或记录失败”放回 `apply_edits` 的主路径语义里，缺文件也应视为一次失败回写并落补偿记录。  
2. forbidden fix patterns to avoid: 继续用 `os.path.exists()` 静默短路；返回成功但不留下任何失败痕迹；新增另一条优先级不明的 fallback 数据源。  
3. requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate

F003  
Severity: HIGH  
Category: test-gap  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: Contract Pack 的关键约束没有被入口级测试保护：回写一致性只测 helper，不测 `apply_edits/edit API`；认证只测“未登录”，不测“无 edit 权限”；school-scope 过滤完全没测。  
After-behavior: 回归测试应在真实入口上覆盖 backwrite、permission negative case 和 school-scope filtering。  
Evidence: [2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2421](C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2421) [2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2422](C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-plan.md#L2422) [test_service.py#L108](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py#L108) [test_router.py#L28](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_router.py#L28) [2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-review-handoff-batch1.md#L36](C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-review-handoff-batch1.md#L36) [2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-review-handoff-batch1.md#L19](C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-07-knowledge-tree-review-handoff-batch1.md#L19)  
Impact: 现在即使删掉 `apply_edits` 的回写调用，或者删掉 school filter，现有测试也很可能照样通过；Contract Pack 的“verification 映射”因此是不准确的。  
Repair hypothesis:  
1. likely repair direction: 用 edit 入口覆盖回写成功/失败两条路径；补 teacher/parent 之类 school-scoped 角色的 mastery 过滤测试；补无 `EDIT_KNOWLEDGE_TREE` 权限的负向测试。  
2. forbidden fix patterns to avoid: 继续只测 helper；继续只用 `platform_admin` 做路由集成测试；只断言 `status_code==200`/`applied==1` 这类弱结果。  
3. requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate

F004  
Severity: MED  
Category: code-bug  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: 设计与工具描述把 `update_node` 限定为“改名/改描述”、`update_edge` 限定为“改关系强度”，但 API schema 接收任意 `fields: dict`，service 又把字段名直接拼进 SQLite `UPDATE`。  
After-behavior: 更新面应严格限制在契约允许的字段集合内。  
Evidence: [schemas.py#L43](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/schemas.py#L43) [knowledge_tree.py#L10](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/knowledge_tree.py#L10) [service.py#L244](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py#L244) [service.py#L271](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py#L271)  
Impact: 有编辑权限的调用方可以提交契约外字段，直接修改 `knowledge_level`、`primary_module` 等未设计的列；更糟的是列名是字符串拼接，错误或恶意字段会把回写 SQL 推到未定义行为。我本地按同样的 SQL 模式复现，`knowledge_level` 能被改成 `L0`，说明这不是理论问题。  
Repair hypothesis:  
1. likely repair direction: 先把每种 op 的可变字段集合定死，再让 PostgreSQL 更新和 SQLite 回写共用同一套字段白名单。  
2. forbidden fix patterns to avoid: 继续接受开放式 `dict`；仅在前端限制字段；继续把列名直接插进 SQL。  
3. requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate

